tter dot or even improve one of our lifetaps would be something well worth the AA points and let us EARN being better.<br><br>I still say we're ok now, but agree we could be better.  I just don't agree that giving up melee damage is worth getting more HP's.<br><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 55 DE Revenant</p>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 62 DE Gravelord<br>Have Axe, will travel</td></td></tr>
