n Tank without taking any damage, which defensive doesn't do (it reduces agro alot).  So basically whenever you get together 2-4 groups of people to do any Raiding, why would you take the chance of NOT having a Tank with Defensive be the Main Assist, it's on par with why would you put a Shaman healing the MA as primary healer.  When the chips go down, everyone does what they have to do, SK's jump in and Tank, Shaman heal, Rangers tank too when they are the last Melee standing and the Clerics haven't camped out yet.<br><br>I'd like to get some plus-up in Tanking, sure, but I don't want to give up Melee ability to do it.  Even if we get buffed up in defense we still will spend most Raids hitting the MOB from behind, so reducing Melee will only make us less useful 90% of the time.<br><br>Neptunis</p>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 62 DE Gravelord<br>Have Axe, will travel</td></td></tr>
