 skills early on.<br><br>However, if you want to train 2HB, then you are FINE for quite some time.  15.25 dmg per sec will leave many drooling over the dmg that you do &amp; you will be fine through your 40s easy.  Further, there are a few 2HB SK weapons that are frightening, but I have seen only ONE so far (Facesmasher if memory serves--they are RARE)<br><br>Anyways, hope this helps<br><br>Lunatic</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
