	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=13385><span id=Scholar>Neptunis</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>278 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.60]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>At 34 you can solo Wolves, Kodiaks, Cougars and Snow Derv's in Eastern Waste along the side of the Bridge.&nbsp;&nbsp;I got quite a few levels there and a few nice earrings too.<br><br>Once you zone into EW head down the bridge, turn to the right then run back along the ground about half way of the ramp up to the bridge.  Make a pet and park him there, then run out and pull stuff back to the pet.  Once you get there fear and pet attack (with Darkness on of course), once fear runs out just run back to where pet started.  The only thing to watch for is the occasional MOB that paths across the end of the bridge.  It's safe to med back along the water as nothing paths there.<br><br>Good luck.<br><br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 55 DE Revenant</p>&nbsp;<br>Neptunis Rex<br>lvl 62 DE Gravelord<br>Have Axe, will travel</td></td></tr>
